{"tid":2069564,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"麻煩大家幫手推 620罷工罷課公投 既行動POST上熱門","createTime":"2020-06-18T13:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T03:48:37.000Z","uid":334720,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dadec96969e8ef96759651964141522ffe30ea0f","tid":2069564,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T13:22:12.000Z","msg":"20號，全港最大三罷公投上線了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2069537/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2069537/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【突發】620公投票站地點出爐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2066484/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2066484/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n工會聯盟既勢力必需盡快建立出黎 <br />\n咁先可以牽制政權<br />\n有工會聯盟勢力既存在<br />\n就唔洗怕所謂槍打出頭鳥<br />\n亦唔洗怕有大少少既勢力就比政府收皮<br />\n因為1個公會退場, 將會有千千萬萬個工會頂上<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">加入工會 全民三罷</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e3b29dd20baff67551b13fe738fa7b1d1ec2a6c","tid":2069564,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T13:24:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"169aea0aa6024d4875b7f5b28506a5537ef0acdb","tid":2069564,"uid":136137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T13:42:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f4882760cd981c8723b04474bad08961828696","tid":2069564,"uid":136137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T13: